Presented by industry expert, Martin Schaeferle, this course is for
developers who want to learn how to integrate COM+ components within a
distributed environment using Microsoft Visual Basic.

Topics include:
** Creating COM component in Visual Basic.
** Learning about COM+ Services.
** Mastering the Component Services Explorer.
** Working with loosely-coupled events.
** Creating n-tier distributed architectures.
** Building transactional component with Microsoft SQL Server.
** Implementing security on the middle tier.
** Integrating Microsoft IIS server with COM+ components.

